getRarityRate(string).details: Get rarity drop rate of the NFT

returns._0: uint8 rarity rate  Rate for Good = 10, Normal = 60, Bad = 30 This means the are 10% chance the user get Good rarity 60% chance the user get Normal rarity 30% chance the user get Bad rarity

safeMint(address).details: Safely mints new NFT and transfers it to `to`.

params._to: this address will be the owner of the NFT.  Emits a Transfer event

params._newTokenUri: the URI of NFT  The URI will be CID of the files
params._tokenId: the token id of NFT that we want to update
